## Installation

```bash
pip install pdag
```

## Usage

See the [`examples`](src/pdag/examples/) directory for usage examples.

## Tests

Run test with:

```bash
dotenvx run -f .env.pytest -- uv run pytest tests
```

or simply

```bash
PYTHONHASHSEED=0 uv run pytest tests
```
